{"tid":274252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【淫賤聯成功爭取...】幼雀掙扎求存 民建聯議員指臭氣薰天認有收投訴","createTime":"2017-06-07T07:42:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-07T08:41:31.000Z","uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8024c46c0264f7593111b61ca34c812fb26ea73f","tid":274252,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T07:42:59.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大埔區民建聯區議員黃碧嬌今日在電台節目表示，事發地點一直有鳥糞問題，形容「臭氣薰天」，途人更不時被鳥糞擊中，承認有接獲不少市民投訴，曾向相關部門反映意見。</span></strong>但今次不肯定署方收到何人投訴而行動，聲言不認同康文署昨日的做法，「今次有可能是1823，自己都收到個別投訴；對今次大量斬樹感到驚訝，在大埔很少見這規模斬樹工程」。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170607/56794567\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170607%2F56794567&d=lWdkQpLmCgxSW1DATsQyGTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=bd6cce5d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170607%2F56794567&h=18bbb759\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170607/56794567</a>"},{"pid":"0e391166c6ec7495bdd8aac93f0e9e26cab13b68","tid":274252,"uid":41821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T08:01:25.000Z","msg":"貓哭老鼠______"},{"pid":"69c34d7401934399c2f94bc6207b70e97bf4fd7d","tid":274252,"uid":7961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T08:41:31.000Z","msg":"跑馬地木球會出面...d雀屎先恐怖"}]}